## RECEIPT SYSTEM

### Purpose
Complete audit trail and operation tracking

### Components (Observed in Operations)
1. **Operation Summary** - What was done
2. **Execution Log** - Phase-by-phase breakdown
3. **Tools Used** - Which tools were employed
